## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="13b18-151">Дополнительные сведения об использовании <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> класса для определения грамматики см. в разделе [Создание грамматик с помощью граммарбуилдер](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/7e2cc577-cb05-4318-9da3-7c8675d3d9ae).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="13b18-151">For more information about using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> class to define a grammar, see [Create Grammars Using GrammarBuilder](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/7e2cc577-cb05-4318-9da3-7c8675d3d9ae).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="13b18-152">В следующем примере создается Грамматика распознавания речи с <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> помощью <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> объектов и.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="13b18-152">The following example creates a speech recognition grammar using <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="13b18-153">Конструктор создает объект из<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder>объекта. <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar.%23ctor%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="13b18-153">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar.%23ctor%2A> constructor creates a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object from the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> object.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
  
// Create a grammar using a GrammarBuilder and return the new grammar.   
private static Grammar CreateGrammarBuilderGrammar()  
{  
  GrammarBuilder builder = new GrammarBuilder();  
  
  Choices cityChoice = new Choices (new string[]   
  {"Seattle", "New York", "Miami", "Los Angeles"});  
  
  builder.Append("I would like to fly from");  
  builder.Append(cityChoice);  
  builder.Append("to");  
  builder.Append(cityChoice);  
  
  Grammar citiesGrammar = new Grammar(builder);  
  citiesGrammar.Name = "GrammarBuilder Cities Grammar";  
  
  return citiesGrammar;  
}  
```

  
  
